T1  - The entrepreneurial journey as an emergent hierarchical system of artifact-creating processes
AU  - Selden, Paul D.
AU  - Fletcher, Denise E.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 30
IS  - 4
SP  - 603
EP  - 615
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/07/01/
